title: Shiba Inu Burn Rate Jumps Nearly 260% in a Day as 53 Million $SHIB Are Removed From Circulation
description: The burn rate of the popular meme-inspired cryptocurrency Shiba Inu ($SHIB) has recently surged more than 250% in just 24 hours after 23 large transactions removed from circulation more than 47.9 million SHIB tokens.
